        "subject": "LU-4538 vvp: cleanup error messages",
        "message": "LU-4538 vvp: cleanup error messages\n\nIn vvp_io_fault_start, this warning:\n\nbinary [FID] changed while waiting for the page fault lock\n\nis logged during many Cray tests.\nThis moves that warning under the D_PAGE debug flag.\n\nIn ldlm_add_waiting_lock, lock debug info and a stack trace\nare printed, and the following message appears:\n\n\"not waiting on destroyed lock (bug 5653)\".\n\nThis removes the stack trace, which is often confused for\na serious error.\n\nChange-Id: I6e294d6b26de925be4d5951ab63cb10cc03d96b3\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <paf@cray.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
